The '''Alderaan Expatriate Network (AEN)''' was a news network set up by [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanian]] expatriates in the wake of the [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destruction]] of their [[Alderaan/Legends|homeworld]]. Many of the staff working for AEN were members of the Alderaanian media who were stationed off-world at the time of the planet's destruction.<ref name="J3" /> The purpose of the network was to spread the truth about the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] attack on their the planet. The network was openly sympathetic to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebellion]] and forwarded any material they could get hold on&mdash;including [[Hologram disc/Legends|holotapes]] of the destruction of Alderaan, recorded by a satellite orbiting [[Delaya/Legends|Delaya]] to other Rebel-affiliated news networks.

